Package: fmseaDatabases
Title: Metabolite and Pathway Databases for fMSEA Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yijiang", "Liu", email = "ejoliu@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Tidymass", "Team", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Curated metabolite MS1 databases and pathway databases
    for Feature-based Metabolite Set Enrichment Analysis (fMSEA).
    This package provides KEGG and HMDB metabolite databases for both
    RP and HILIC columns, as well as pathway databases from KEGG and Reactome.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
